![Towing](https://via.placeholder.com/600x400/000000/FF6600?text=Towing+Service)  
24/7 flatbed or tow truck service

## Competitive Analysis – SWOT

| Player              | Strengths                                      | Weaknesses                                   | Opportunities                                      | Threats                                          |
|---------------------|------------------------------------------------|----------------------------------------------|----------------------------------------------------|--------------------------------------------------|
| **ReadyAssist**     | Strong in major cities, 24/7 helpline, wide network | Limited minor repairs, inconsistent pricing  | Smaller cities, mobile app, dealership partnerships | Rising competition, fuel cost impact             |
| **Allianz Assistance** | Pan-India, multilingual, cashless transactions | Slower response, heavy partner dependency    | Insurance bundling, preventive maintenance         | Regulations, partner capacity issues             |
| **GoMechanic**      | Transparent pricing, large workshop network    | Limited on-site quality control              | Integrated services, new cities                    | Larger players entering app-based space          |
| **Crossroads**      | 24/7 helpline, free estimates                  | Limited coverage area, towing-focused        | Additional services, car rental tie-ups            | Customer shift to modern mobile apps             |

**QUICK FIX Opportunity**  
Fill the gap with:  
- Fast mobile-first booking & real-time tracking  
- Transparent & flexible pricing  
- Strong focus on Tier-2/3 cities  
- Integrated partner quality control

## Primary Research Sources

- Car owners & drivers (urban + semi-urban)  
- On-field mechanics & service providers  
- Repair workshop owners  

