**Project Goal**  
Create a modern, reliable, and user-friendly digital roadside assistance ecosystem that turns stressful breakdowns into quick, confident recoveries.

**Next Steps (Suggested for Development)**  
- High-fidelity mobile app screens (booking flow, live tracking, service history)  
- Partner dashboard for mechanics/workshops  
- Subscription model exploration  
- Integration with insurance APIs & payment gateways

